      • pingHttpURL

        public static boolean pingHttpURL(java.lang.String url)
        Opens an HTTP connection to a web URL and tests that the response is a valid 200-level code and we can successfully open a stream to the content.
        Parameters:
        url - The HTTP URL indicating the location of the content.
        Returns:
        True if the content can be accessed successfully, false otherwise.
